bianxiao cui lab stanford cui lab stanford department of chemistry stanford university _____________________________________________________________ home people research publications news&views contactus intraweb single molecule neurobiology welcome to cui lab at the chemistry department of the stanford university our research interest lies in the understanding the signal propagation in neurons using quantitative tools developed by physical sciences we focus on the long distance transport of vesicular cargoes in axons and its implication in neurodegenerative diseases methods of interest include single molecule fluorescence imaging magnetic and optical trapping multi layer soft lithography microfluidic neuronal network and planar micro electrode patterning copyright 2008 bianxiao cui all rights reserved designed by free css templates
